      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 15:30:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加州资源公司将以 21 亿美元收购 Aera Energy</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/california-resources-to-buy-aera-energy-in-2-1-billion-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[石油生产商加州资源公司 (California Resources Corp.) 将收购 Aera Energy LLC，这笔交易使该公司估值约为 21 亿美元（包括债务），从而在西部州建立其钻探投资组合。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/california-resources-to-buy-aera-energy-in-2-1-billion-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 14:56:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
