      <title>商业地产困境加剧，KKR 抵押房地产投资信托基金暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/kkr-mortgage-reit-falls-after-cutting-dividend-on-troubled-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资商业抵押贷款的 KKR 房地产金融信托公司 (KKR Real Estate Finance Trust Inc.) 在削减股息以帮助其处理不良贷款后，股价暴跌。]]></description>
